                            <comment id="13809485" author="beobal" created="Wed, 30 Oct 2013 18:57:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Actually, this problem is present in earlier versions than 1.2.10, as &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5555&quot; title=&quot;Allow sstableloader to handle a larger number of files&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-5555&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-5555&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; was actually included in 1.2.7&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
